          <li>You have the legal capacity to enter into agreements.</li>
          <li>Information provided is accurate and complete.</li>
          <li>You will comply with applicable laws and regulations.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="legal-section">
        <h2>4. User Accounts</h2>
        <p>Where account registration is available:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>You are responsible for maintaining account security.</li>
          <li>You are responsible for activities conducted through your account.</li>
          <li>You must notify us immediately of unauthorized access.</li>
